Broken code:
```scala
class Test[A](implicit val m: Manifest[A]) 
class Foo 
object Bar extends Test[Foo] 
Bar.m 
```

Work around 1: 
`(new Test[Foo]).m`

Work around 2:
```scala
class Test[A](implicit m: Manifest[A]) {
    val foo = m
} 
object Bar extends Test[Foo] 
Bar.foo 
```
